		<h2>Classified Listings</h2>
		<p>While building homes (yes, it's true, we are home builders) one of the things we became aware of was that the amount of items in our storage seemed to increase with each home we built.  These items were usually new (or almost new), but couldn't be returned to the supplier, so they went in storage.  So, the first project we worked on was <a href="http://www.buildswap.com" alt="Buy and sell new and used materials, tools, and equipment">BuildSwap</a>.  BuildSwap is a hybrid between craigslist and eBay built specifically for the home building industry allowing users to buy and sell new and used building materials, tools, and equipment.</p>
